      <abstract obkms_id="5b5fbce4-a7a9-4daf-9d9c-c490ae809bc8" obkms_process="TRUE">
        <label>Abstract</label>
        <p>Five new supraspecific taxa of Scapania are proposed, <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="6d5ae348-cb03-42a3-9f38-8dcb77c9a6cf" obkms_process="TRUE">Scapania</tp:taxon-name></italic> subg. <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="6860ab54-a197-46f1-a511-0ac933e00f0c" obkms_process="TRUE">Gracilidae</tp:taxon-name></italic>, <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="81e1a83e-9713-4d73-8976-4c1c2c3069ce" obkms_process="TRUE">Scapania</tp:taxon-name></italic> subg. <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="8c84c2b3-5d1f-4943-ade2-3dfd33ef652d" obkms_process="TRUE">Pseudomacrodiplophyllum</tp:taxon-name></italic>, <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="1c91afa2-78ed-4e31-90aa-98a8f49ce6b5" obkms_process="TRUE">Scapania</tp:taxon-name></italic> sect. <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="44049184-c865-4065-b776-4ea64c5439d8" obkms_process="TRUE">Americanae</tp:taxon-name></italic>, <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="901276c8-50cc-48e3-9836-44181864c09d" obkms_process="TRUE">Scapania</tp:taxon-name></italic> sect. <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="34502711-8529-45a7-9989-46b248c90c94" obkms_process="TRUE">Hyperboreae</tp:taxon-name></italic>, and <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="a19e85de-9070-4f02-aa7b-9c0b89889c57" obkms_process="TRUE">Scapania</tp:taxon-name></italic> sect. <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="7e0cbb7d-728f-4222-a0af-65f21b9ece60" obkms_process="TRUE">Simmonsia</tp:taxon-name></italic>.</p>
      </abstract>
